  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "0ba6705c73d2559973e964b14d0d4a820959d20c5d04f8dd0515c781a8c0cf6a": "You are a good human, [?].",
    "1bf60ac19e6496b6f3418a5fddc25939f7c5f66b882eb352d6725be80f4b17d2": "What do you say then, [?]? Do you want to help the Black Guard with this?",
    "1e3336a473c550a715dab858548e12f100ac97cccee8d21a0e476635257b974c": "I see... I cannot make that decision, I'm afraid. Speak to the director of [?], he may be able to help you.",
    "32024d71246291f81ce7f0a7a3b9f75f7c1af6c3e0bf1c5fd2f52f56ad29901f": "What news from the Consortium, [?]?",
    "3eace1498861b7fa849ff28df770dd561b071c5f02c3595de8285a59dd241614": "How are you getting on with rebuilding our statue, [?]?",
    "544cab03d7fac652e9dddcc533d803a702f04d39d4904456549e78d59e1012fe": "[?], I thought you had something important to tell me?",
    "620c20e8d7a8de166de11d0c92818b8e530b8c2f1ff88ed9a3f870b7d37f9333": "Well then, [?], what is it going to be?",
    "75898a56d2d4f8e98fcd34dd59dbaf5cc91f845a5e0aca99f57fa7e30bab4cd8": "[?], are you absolutely sure? You might not get another chance like this. Are you sure you just want to read the summary of the meeting instead of seeing the actual meeting?",
    "ac47469f6f559dcfc3249792a1a10aee083fa9b9cfaf0dcf91b1bdde1d7bc428": "What is it, [?]?",
    "b02dafa6745e9ed44b0087558d6676b26e4d8d4b439c4d01f818a5d98f434459": "Don't worry, [?], I believe you. You must have been put under a spell of some sort to make you forget.",
    "be041425deb098424533a120746d236854e0e97048bea05278e5b44ee6e33b16": "Not at the moment, no, [?].",
    "beeb39d11e61d4ade76643cd5fe83c15818b8a19b346c5b9f64f763c5d2e6f7d": "Poor [?], I think you've been bewitched.",
    "c5a2decb8f998d32c85111ef0c9c9bd54dfe5fffc2039d966c45a6fc796d43d0": "[?]! Have you heard?",
    "c8dc066147f2be7adb4aa0ec5af6ea069bcd9bf94e6f4cd6bbe86f34edfa5e48": "What happened, [?], did you finish your assignment?",
    "f0a67e0ec4e1375e11891c74096d765f0046a491586d33b93aebac1a4e5c0cf2": "Happy to hear that, [?]! Please go and check it out!"
  }
